For each tree:

1. check if tree next door is higher or not
2. If adjacent tree is higher then tree is totally INVISIBLE from that direction -
   MOVE ON TO NEXT DIRECTION FOR SAME tree   (Next CHECK BLOCK of CODE)
3. If adjacent tree not higher then move on to CHECK NEXT TREE IN SAME DIRECTION.  (Continue statement)
4. IF get to the end of row and tree is still VISIBLE then mark '1' on visibility grid 
   and MOVE ON TO NEXT 'd' (next Tree to check for visibility) - BREAK Commands and final Continue for 'd'.